##EXAMPLES##:
        ==nuts== {{search}} **--help**
            shows this help and exit
       
        ==nuts== {{search}}
            search installed nuts

        ==nuts== {{search}} **--offline** netbeans-\*
            search all components that start with "netbeans-" in all local repositories

        ==nuts== {{search}} **--anywhere** netbeans-\*
            search all components that start with "netbeans-" in all local and remote repositories
